    "name": "骰子对决",
    "steam_appid": 3008180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《骰子对决》，一个将紧张刺激的回合制战斗与充满变数的 Roguelike 冒险完美融合的世界！在这里，运气是基础，策略才是王道。你将扮演<strong>骰术士罗德</strong>，踏上拯救世界的旅程，运用智慧操控骰子的力量，对抗诡谲多变的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次冒险都是全新的挑战：随机生成的技能、遭遇的敌人、以及发现的神秘装置，都将塑造你独一无二的战斗风格。从阴险的盗贼到空洞的骷髅，从嗜血的吸血鬼伯爵到奇异的狼人...你将面对一系列光怪陆离的对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心玩法：</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗围绕“骰子”展开！敌我双方的行动都取决于骰子的点数。但别担心，这绝非纯靠运气！在战斗开始前，你可以<strong>探查敌人的技能</strong>，并利用<strong>自己收集到的技能</strong>，对即将掷出的<strong>双方骰子点数进行精妙的修改</strong>。是强化自己？还是削弱敌人？每一次决策都关乎生死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更重要的是，在冒险中发现<strong>威力强大装置</strong>——<strong>只有成功撤离，才能将本次获得的装置安全带回，用于下一次至关重要的旅程！</strong> 在<strong>安全屋</strong>中，你甚至可以将已有的装置<strong>合成为更强大、更独特</strong>的新装备。打造强大的技能与装置组合，运用智慧掌控骰局与撤离时机，在这个由骰子主宰的世界中杀出一条生路吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能否拯救世界，就看你的抉择了！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>骰子驱动的核心战斗：</strong> 攻击、技能发动，一切皆由骰子点数决定，带来独特的紧张感和策略深度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/793ecde386466980453360d97952855d.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/793ecde386466980453360d97952855d.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/793ecde386466980453360d97952855d.mp4?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略至上，掌控命运：</strong> 在战斗前探查敌人技能，并利用自身技能对敌我双方的骰子点数进行<strong>关键性修改</strong>，将运气转化为可控的策略优势。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/00acfc747f6960cc41e2f85c17db2774.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/00acfc747f6960cc41e2f85c17db2774.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/00acfc747f6960cc41e2f85c17db2774.mp4?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>刺激的搜打撤循环 (探索-战斗-撤离)：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong>充满机遇与危险的世界，发现<strong>神秘装置</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗</strong>并运用策略击败敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成功撤离</strong>是<strong>保留并带走本次冒险所得装置</strong>的唯一途径！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>撤离失败将丢失所有未保护的装置</strong>——<strong>安全箱</strong>是保护关键装置的最后防线。</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/b4eb3b1c7485e1069ba088d564c36cdd.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/b4eb3b1c7485e1069ba088d564c36cdd.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装置合成与成长：</strong> 在<strong>安全屋</strong>中，将冒险带回的装置<strong>合成为更强大、更独特</strong>的装备，不断提升你的战斗力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/fedf62e3bcf77b2294bf73c807473838.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/fedf62e3bcf77b2294bf73c807473838.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/fedf62e3bcf77b2294bf73c807473838.mp4?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike 冒险体验：</strong> 每次旅程都独一无二！随机生成的技能、敌人、事件、装置和撤离点，保证每一次冒险都充满新鲜感、挑战和紧张刺激的撤离抉择。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/52d5b40229f72d5acc26b0b839941b2b.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/52d5b40229f72d5acc26b0b839941b2b.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造专属构筑：</strong> 在冒险过程中收集五花八门的<strong>技能</strong>和<strong>装置</strong>，自由组合搭配，形成属于你自己的独特战斗流派。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/e94cb9a675b6a0f75daa1c326f1dccf9.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/e94cb9a675b6a0f75daa1c326f1dccf9.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/e94cb9a675b6a0f75daa1c326f1dccf9.mp4?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战风格迥异的敌人：</strong> 对战狡诈的盗贼、诡异的骷髅、强大的吸血鬼伯爵、神秘的狼人等各具特色的敌人，每个敌人都需要不同的应对策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/c84e76d9df7c2f23d5354046a49c00a6.poster.avif?t=1758727731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/c84e76d9df7c2f23d5354046a49c00a6.webm?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008180/extras/c84e76d9df7c2f23d5354046a49c00a6.mp4?t=1758727731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
